Build requirements:
===================

This code was written and tested using the following libraries and
versions:

* GCC - 4.4.5
* SDL - 1.2.14
* SDL_mixer - 1.2.8
* OpenAL - 1.12

The packages in Debian is called:

* libsdl1.2debian
* libsdl1.2-dev
* libsdl-mixer1.2
* libsdl-mixer1.2-dev
* libopenal1
* libopenal-dev

Install these in Debian Squeeze using:

$ sudo apt-get install libsdl1.2debian libsdl1.2-dev libsdl-mixer1.2 libsdl-mixer1.2-dev libopenal1 libopenal-dev


Build instructions:
===================

You may need to make changes in the Makefile.

Build a debug binary using (default):

$ make debug

Build a release binary using:

$ make release

